  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db8\u0dad\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wimal's opinion is also said",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "National Freedom Front leader MP Wimal Weerawansa said that the President and the Prime Minister should bow down to the aspirations of the people and resign.",
        "The MP then said that efforts should be made to establish an interim government that would be accepted locally as well as internationally, while confirming the political position of the country and also stated that solving the economic problem should play a leading role."
      ],
